      <title>鲍威尔押注 9 月降息，美国国债价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/treasuries-rally-as-powell-locks-in-bets-on-a-september-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆鲍威尔在杰克逊霍尔的讲话巩固了人们对央行下个月降息的预期后，美国国债价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/treasuries-rally-as-powell-locks-in-bets-on-a-september-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦铀矿产量预期“未达标” 铀矿公司股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/investors-rush-into-uranium-miners-on-kazakh-production-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球最大的铀生产商哈萨克斯坦国家原子能公司 (Kazatomprom) 发布的业绩指引不及市场预期后，北美专注于铀资源的投资者纷纷大举购买核反应堆燃料矿业公司的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/investors-rush-into-uranium-miners-on-kazakh-production-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 13:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔暗示降息，新兴市场资产上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席鲍威尔表示调整货币政策的时机已经到来，新兴市场股市和货币随之上涨，带动风险资产上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 10:36:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金矿公司第二次削减产量目标后股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/gold-fields-cuts-target-again-on-chile-south-africa-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于智利和南非矿山的运营困难，Gold Fields Ltd. 在不到三个月内第二次下调了产量预期，股价创下 10 周以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/gold-fields-cuts-target-again-on-chile-south-africa-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 07:20:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GE Vernova 股价因另一起海上风电叶片故障而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/ge-vernova-sees-another-blade-failure-at-uk-offshore-wind-farm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通用电气 Vernova 公司股价周五暴跌近 7%，原因是该公司位于英格兰附近的一个海上风电场的一片涡轮叶片发生故障，这是该公司设备发生的一系列事故中的最新一起，这些事故损害了公众对陷入困境的行业的认可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/ge-vernova-sees-another-blade-failure-at-uk-offshore-wind-farm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 23:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
